manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: OlarHike Packing Cube sets offer a variety of sizes to make packing and organizing a breeze! Available in various colors and patterns, purchase multiple sets to color-coordinate and stay sorted in style.

Packing cubes allows you to save valuable suitcase space and time when on-the-go. These light-weight cubes fit most standard size suitcases, and keeps all your clothing and traveling essentials easily accessible and at your fingertips.

Sturdy, two-way zippers for smooth sliding closures, that reduces the risk jamming or snagging. Durable double stitching protects from tearing Rip and tear resistant breathable mesh, keeps clothing fresh and easily visible.
Icons located on the outside of each cube help you to easily place or identify contents.

Versatile and convenient, storage cubes help you to stay sorted in any setting. OlarHike Packing Cubes can be used to stay organized at home, while traveling, and are perfect for camping or any outdoor adventure!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wow! Heavy duty space savers
reviews.reviewText: I recently returned from a week long trip using these OlarHike packing cubes for the first time. For background, I am a packing nerd. I begin gathering my clothing, shoes, and dodads about a week before a major trip. I thought I was an efficient packer by tightly rolling most of my clothing and stashing smalls in nooks and crannies. Boy was I wrong. OlarHike packing cubes are a game changer. I had previously ordered another set of packing cubes and was deeply disappointed in the quality of that set and was happy to get a refund. Flimsy, small, didn't look like they would hold up for long. I kept looking and found OH's set for only $5 more which included more cubes, a shoe bag, and dirty laundry bag. The cubes are spacious. The venting beneficial. The zippers heavy-duty compared to others I have seen. The reviews with photos were very helpful, and I'm sorry I don't have photos from this trip. I split the packages between two suitcases--a 28-inch double-sided checked bag and a 20-inch carry-on. Superb organization. One benefit I hadn't considered was the benefits when unpacking once I returned home. Previously, I would open my suitcases, unpack clothing into a laundry basket and haul it to the laundry room. This time around, I simply picked up the packing cubes and easily carried them to the laundry to wash. Easy and simple. I am very happy with these cubes and believe you will be too. BUY THEM! The value for price is astounding.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality for the cheap price
reviews.reviewText: These packing cubes have quickly become an indispensable part of my travel routine. The level of organization they provide is truly remarkable. With different sizes to accommodate various items, I can neatly separate and categorize my clothes, accessories, and other essentials. No more digging through a chaotic suitcase!The quality of the packing cubes is outstanding for the cost of them. The fabric is durable, and the zippers glide smoothly without any snagging. I appreciate the construction, which ensures that the cubes maintain their shape even when packed to capacity. They have shown no signs of wear, even after multiple trips.One of the standout features is the space-saving advantage. The cubes allow for efficient use of suitcase space, maximizing the capacity and reducing the need for excessive folding or rearranging. It's incredible how much more I can fit into my luggage without it becoming an unorganized mess.Another notable benefit is the convenience they offer during unpacking. Instead of rifling through my entire suitcase to find a specific item, I simply need to locate the relevant cube. It saves time and eliminates the frustration of searching for things amidst the chaos.Additionally, the breathable mesh panels allow for easy identification of the contents without having to open each cube. This feature comes in handy when I need quick access to specific items or when going through airport security checks.
